name: D E T H E R A B A S A T H
description:
[SIMULATANEON SERIES #009]

D E T H E R A B A S A T H

Mass bludeoning devices exist in most geopolitical epicenters. Some hidden, some known. Some disciplinary, some lethal. You will go to great lengths to dodge their untimely swings.

SIMULATANEON is a 2017 hypersigil and a conceptual prison break map for the upcoming matrix system update. The sigils that were borrowed for this series reveal only part of a bigger tapestry.
